When police visited Mr Almanza's house in the island's capital of Palma de Mallorca, they found the body expertly chopped up and the parts stored in a chest freezer.

The secodn gruesome discovery came when they opened his kitchen fridge-freezer, finding that he had stored his brother's head and other parts below shelves filled with fresh food.

Mr Almanza claims he murdered his brother after Osmas had tried to attack him with a hammer during a fight,

Almanza said he had offered his brother a place to stay when he fell on hard times, but that they had frequently argued, escalating into a physical attack ending in Osmas's death.

